						               													<description>- There is little left for the next full moon. When it shines high in the sky, the secret conclave of the potion-makers order of warlocks and withes will begin. Then, the oldest and wisest of the master witches and warlocks, will choose from among the aspirants, the new member of the order, to whom all kinds of secrets will be revealed. Only one will be chosen. -&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As an aspirant, you will have to brew as many potions as possible to prove your skills and convince the council of elders. But don't worry, you have your magical helpers, who will make it easier for you to collect ingredients. In addition, you know the formula of the multipurpose potion that will be of great help to you.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Potions is a simple roll and write game, easy to explain and play, with some interaction between players, dice draft, push your luck and set collection.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;On your turn you roll the 6 dice, which you can reroll up to 2 times. Then you will choose a value and you will take all the dice with that value that you will spend in the best way to complete the ingredients of the potions. Players will be able to make use of the abilities of their helpers to facilitate their task. Also the more complicated potions will provide bonuses.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
